OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F2,160 bus routes cut in    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FEngland, campaigners say   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Axing bus routes in England leaves     
OL,6, communities "cut off" from essential   
OL,7, services and interactions, campaigners 
OL,8, have warned.                           
OL,10,FThe latest official data shows a       
OL,11,Freduction of 2,160 bus routes, or      
OL,12,Fnearly 20%, between 2022 and 2023.     
OL,14,FLabour accused the government of       
OL,15,F"vandalism against communities" and    
OL,16,Fsaid more services were at risk.       
OL,18,FThe Department for Transport said the  
OL,19,Fincrease was partly down to changes in 
OL,20,Fthe bus licensing system.              
